25 min
Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil.
In a large skillet over medium heat saut√© the garlic and anchovies in the olive oil until garlic is golden.
Add the tomatoes, olives and capers. Cook on medium heat for 15-20 minutes, until reduced.
Cook the spaghetti until al dente (about 2 minutes less than directions) and drain it.
Add to the tomato sauce and mix to thoroughly combine.
Serve immediately garnished with parsley.
